            "chapterTitle": "Excellence of Leading an Ascetic Life, and Virtues of Simple Life",
            "urn": 1604850,
            "body": "<p>Usamah bin Zaid (May Allah be pleased with them) reported: The Prophet (\ufdfa) said, \"I stood at the gate of Jannah and saw that most of those who enter it were poor, whereas the rich were held back; but those who were destined to go to Hell were ordered to be sent there (immediately).\"<br/><br/><b>[Al-Bukhari and Muslim]</b>.</p>",
